---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/astro/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/astro/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - ServDubai" description="ServDubai terms of service and conditions for using our building maintenance and repair services in Dubai, UAE.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Terms of Service Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto container-padding">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These terms and conditions govern your use of ServDubai's services. Please read them carefully before using our services.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
          <p>Last updated: January 2024</p>
          <p>Effective date: January 1, 2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 card-shadow prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          By accessing or using ServDubai's services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations. 
          If you do not agree with any of these terms, you are prohibited from using our services.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Description of Services</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">ServDubai provides comprehensive building maintenance and repair services including but not limited to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>HVAC Services:</strong> Air conditioning installation, maintenance, and repair</li>
          <li><strong>Plumbing Services:</strong> Pipe repair, fixture installation, and emergency plumbing</li>
          <li><strong>Electrical Services:</strong> Electrical repairs, installation, and safety inspections</li>
          <li><strong>Painting Services:</strong> Interior and exterior painting and touch-ups</li>
          <li><strong>General Maintenance:</strong> Routine building maintenance and repairs</li>
          <li><strong>Emergency Services:</strong> 24/7 emergency repair services</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Service Bookings and Appointments</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Booking Process</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Service requests can be made through our website, phone, or WhatsApp</li>
          <li>All bookings are subject to technician availability</li>
          <li>We will confirm appointments within 2 hours of booking</li>
          <li>Emergency services are prioritized and may affect standard appointment schedules</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Appointment Changes</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Customers may reschedule appointments with at least 4 hours notice</li>
          <li>ServDubai reserves the right to reschedule due to emergencies or unforeseen circumstances</li>
          <li>Cancellations made less than 2 hours before the appointment may incur a service fee</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Pricing and Payment</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Service Pricing</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Pricing is based on service type, complexity, and materials required</li>
          <li>Estimates are provided before work begins and are valid for 30 days</li>
          <li>Additional work beyond the original scope requires customer approval</li>
          <li>Emergency service rates may apply for after-hours calls</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Payment Terms</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Payment is due upon completion of services unless otherwise agreed</li>
          <li>We accept cash, bank transfer, and major credit cards</li>
          <li>AMC contracts require quarterly payments in advance</li>
          <li>Overdue accounts may be subject to interest charges and collection fees</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">New Resident Discounts</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>New residents are eligible for discounts up to 30% on first services</li>
          <li>Proof of residency may be required to qualify for discounts</li>
          <li>Discounts cannot be combined with other offers unless specified</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Annual Maintenance Contracts (AMC)</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Contract Terms</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>AMC contracts are valid for 12 months from the start date</li>
          <li>Services included are specified in the individual contract agreement</li>
          <li>Priority scheduling is provided for AMC customers</li>
          <li>Contracts automatically renew unless cancelled with 30 days notice</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Included Services</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Regular preventive maintenance as scheduled</li>
          <li>Emergency repair services within contract scope</li>
          <li>Parts and materials for covered services</li>
          <li>Annual system inspections and reports</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Exclusions</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Services outside the contract scope require separate charges</li>
          <li>Damage due to misuse, negligence, or external factors</li>
          <li>Replacement of equipment beyond repair</li>
          <li>Upgrades or modifications not specified in the contract</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Service Warranties and Guarantees</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Workmanship Warranty</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>All labor is guaranteed for 90 days from completion</li>
          <li>Parts are covered under manufacturer warranty</li>
          <li>Warranty does not cover normal wear and tear</li>
          <li>Warranty is void if unauthorized modifications are made</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Customer Satisfaction</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>We guarantee satisfaction with our work and service</li>
          <li>Issues must be reported within 48 hours of service completion</li>
          <li>We will return to address warranty issues at no additional cost</li>
          <li>Refunds may be provided for unsatisfactory work at our discretion</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
        
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Provide safe and reasonable access to work areas</li>
          <li><strong>Information:</strong> Provide accurate information about the property and issues</li>
          <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Ensure a safe working environment free from hazards</li>
          <li><strong>Utilities:</strong> Ensure necessary utilities (water, electricity) are available</li>
          <li><strong>Preparation:</strong> Clear work areas of personal belongings and obstacles</li>
          <li><strong>Supervision:</strong> Ensure pets and children are secured during service</li>
          <li><strong>Payment:</strong> Pay for services according to agreed terms</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          ServDubai's liability is limited to the cost of services provided. We are not liable for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
          <li>Loss of business, profits, or data</li>
          <li>Damage to property not directly related to our work</li>
          <li>Issues arising from pre-existing conditions not disclosed</li>
          <li>Damage caused by acts of nature, accidents, or third parties</li>
          <li>Delays due to circumstances beyond our control</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">Insurance Coverage</h4>
          <p class="text-yellow-800 text-sm">
            ServDubai maintains appropriate insurance coverage for our operations. However, customers are encouraged 
            to maintain their own property insurance to cover potential damages.
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Emergency Services</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">24/7 Emergency Response</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Emergency services are available 24/7 for urgent situations</li>
          <li>Emergency rates apply for after-hours, weekend, and holiday services</li>
          <li>Response time goals: 2 hours for emergencies, 4 hours for urgent issues</li>
          <li>Emergency classification is determined by ServDubai based on safety and urgency</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Emergency Situations Include</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Water leaks causing property damage</li>
          <li>Electrical issues posing safety hazards</li>
          <li>HVAC failures in extreme weather conditions</li>
          <li>Security-related issues (locks, doors)</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Your privacy is important to us. Our collection, use, and protection of personal information is governed by our 
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a>, 
          which is incorporated into these terms by reference.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Complaint Process</h3>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Contact our customer service team immediately</li>
          <li>Provide detailed information about the issue</li>
          <li>Allow reasonable time for investigation and resolution</li>
          <li>Escalate to management if initial resolution is unsatisfactory</li>
        </ol>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Governing Law</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          These terms are governed by the laws of the United Arab Emirates. Any disputes will be resolved through 
          the courts of Dubai, UAE, or through binding arbitration as mutually agreed.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          ServDubai reserves the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon 
          posting on our website. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Contact Information</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          For questions about these terms or our services, please contact us:
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Customer Service</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                <span class="block">Phone: <a href="tel:+971501234567" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">+971 50 123 4567</a></span>
                <span class="block">WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/971501234567" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">+971 50 123 4567</a></span>
                <span class="block">Email: <a href="mailto:info@servdubai.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">info@servdubai.com</a></span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Emergency Services</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                <span class="block">24/7 Hotline: <a href="tel:+971501234567" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">+971 50 123 4567</a></span>
                <span class="block">Emergency WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/971501234567?text=EMERGENCY" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Emergency Chat</a></span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Business Address</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              ServDubai Building Maintenance Services<br>
              Dubai, United Arab Emirates<br>
              Business License: [License Number]
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200">

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Agreement Acknowledgment</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm">
            By using ServDubai's services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. 
            If you have any questions about these terms, please contact us before using our services.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4 sm:flex sm:justify-center">
          <a href="/privacy" class="block sm:inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">
            Privacy Policy
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="block sm:inline-block bg-white text-primary-600 border border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors">
            Schedule Site Visit
          </a>
          <a href="/" class="block sm:inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
